des: Reynolds Community Radio is a radio channel of music and information custom made for the Reynolds Lake Oconee neighborhood. The music playlist includes feel good favorites from the 70s, 80s, 90s and 00s. The channel also features various specialty music programs, sponsor and community information making this channel extremely unique to the Reynolds Lake Oconee area.
